{"tid":1253663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"626 希望大家再次出黎","createTime":"2019-06-23T16:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T16:48:35.000Z","uid":257834,"like":80,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b90794c19e6758def46bda4e35532630eeec8f11","tid":1253663,"uid":257834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:38:21.000Z","msg":"大家有冇發現政府宣布咗暫緩修例之後 <br />\n好多人 特別係中立人士 已經接受咗呢樣野 <br />\n好似當無事發生 <br />\n慢慢又過翻啲正常生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一方面 大家記唔記得612其中一樣最大迴響嘅野係咩？<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警濫權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n如果我地可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">focus係黑警濫權呢個point</span><br />\n強調成立<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獨立調查委員會</span><br />\n集中翻啲民意 吸納多啲人支持 <br />\n然後先再延伸翻去我地原本嘅五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解係626？<br />\n1) 626係臨近G20<br />\n我地一定要多啲人再次企出黎<br />\n話俾國際社會聽 就算暫緩修例 有好多問題都未解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 民陣吹咗雞 迴響應該大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家呢幾日可以做多啲文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1) 除咗社區放映 我地都可以airdrop多啲黑警暴力片段俾其他人 煽動翻民眾情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個真心work 上次係街睇黑警暴力片放映 睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 文宣可以強調 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際特赦組織已經證實班黑警係有濫用武力</span><br />\n無論整長輩圖定ig/fb share都好 <br />\n而家直到626個日都要不停宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家唔好忘記當日班黑警點對手無寸鐵嘅市民<br />\n唔好俾件事停</span><br />\n有意見可以一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補翻朱凱迪整嘅黑警暴行集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nshorturl.at/qyB29<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/go5BuwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgo5BuwW.png&h=315f6d61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTN0WbX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTN0WbX.png&h=9bc24f82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ee6d9a777ca373c34b457974c753422eb5462c0","tid":1253663,"uid":257834,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得中信大廈件事可以著力宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/13eauJMTOkU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F13eauJMTOkU&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=efae47cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/13eauJMTOkU</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以po翻612當日啲相/片方便大家互相share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7658bb0de117e4639d27b6a79e7b24aef97362","tid":1253663,"uid":257834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:45:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40a392ac151f58fb74e77b7c387defaef88b8a9e","tid":1253663,"uid":257834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:45:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b42c8ff4e5a19b811f5577a7222932c27a837c44","tid":1253663,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:45:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ab7d84acc12a450ad2581f8d37cca2ff019ec87","tid":1253663,"uid":50835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bdc5f82e8c